imdb.plot outline: Rey Mysterio is WWE's preeminent giant- killer. Staring up at nearly all of his competition, what he lacks in size he makes up tenfold in heart and determination. With an innovative offensive attack highlighted by the gravity-defying 619, this ultimate underdog has proven time and time again why he is pound-for-pound one of the most accomplished Superstars of all time. This special collection from WWE compiles the best edge-of-your-seat action from the masked Superstar including his grueling Steel Cage match vs Batista, high flying classics against CM Punk, Chris Jericho and more!
imdb.title: WWE Superstar Collection Rey Mysterio
